    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《书剑恩仇录》一款融合了高自由度可编程技能和类暗黑刷装局外成长的轻肉鸽爽快动作游戏。自由解构、搭配、重塑江湖武学，体验 “自创武功” 的宗师成就感（基于《庖丁解牛拳》哲学设计）。海量装备可局外继承强化，兼顾 “刷宝乐趣” 与 “累积成长”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自定义连招与必杀技系统：可派生不同招式、自由镶嵌秘籍，连招越长内力消耗越低；角色在不同武器下有独立动作模组，操作反馈清晰，还能定制专属战斗风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/a759ed6130be1fa0864cd93ee1d6176f.poster.avif?t=1771693055\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/a759ed6130be1fa0864cd93ee1d6176f.webm?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/a759ed6130be1fa0864cd93ee1d6176f.mp4?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/b0742515305af3bdb79c426c77680f8f.poster.avif?t=1771693055\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/b0742515305af3bdb79c426c77680f8f.webm?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/b0742515305af3bdb79c426c77680f8f.mp4?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/b0742515305af3bdb79c426c77680f8f.poster.avif?t=1771693055\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/b0742515305af3bdb79c426c77680f8f.webm?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/b0742515305af3bdb79c426c77680f8f.mp4?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >强交互感战斗：拥有完整韧性机制，敌我均受格挡、硬直等状态影响；攻击可触发浮空等控效，搭配高反应 NPC，鼓励玩家灵活运用闪避、反击等机制应对。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/6a40d3e5a1a975dadfed58175ee64f36.poster.avif?t=1771693055\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/6a40d3e5a1a975dadfed58175ee64f36.webm?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/6a40d3e5a1a975dadfed58175ee64f36.mp4?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >轻肉鸽玩法：局内战斗机制随机，必杀技秘籍单局随机获取且离局重置，不影响角色基础数值；局外装备、资源类道具可永久保留，用于角色长期养成。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/435ffd15635103c0ebbb3e419af2adf3.poster.avif?t=1771693055\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/435ffd15635103c0ebbb3e419af2adf3.webm?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1541810/extras/435ffd15635103c0ebbb3e419af2adf3.mp4?t=1771693055\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
